ces, application modernization, cybersecurity, and blockchain solutions. It serves healthcare, life sciences, manufacturing, banking and financial, transport logistics sectors. The company was formerly known as 8K Miles Software Services Limited and changed its name to SecureKloud Technologies Limited in January 2021. SecureKloud Technologies Limited was incorporated in 1985 and is based in Chennai, India."}}